last_episode_to_air.name: Episode Two
last_episode_to_air.overview: As an `Iron Curtain' fell across Europe, the jet bomber came to define how the Cold War was fought. Able to fly faster, higher and further than ever before, and armed with a devastating new weapon, Britain's V Force became the platform for delivering nuclear Armageddon.

name: Cold War, Hot Jets
overview: A tv series looking at the many jet aircrafts of the Cold War era and the rolls they played.
